[[日本|日本]]從1956年首次提名[[日本電影|日本電影]]角逐[[奧斯卡最佳國際影片獎|奧斯卡最佳國際影片獎]]競賽，由[[市川崑|市川崑]]所執導的《[[緬甸的豎琴|緬甸的豎琴]]》是日本首部參加奧斯卡最佳外語片獎的[[電影|電影]]。目前，由[[日本映畫製作者聯盟|日本映畫製作者聯盟]]決定每年日本的參賽電影。奧斯卡最佳外語片獎為[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]中頒發給年度最佳非[[英語|英語]]電影的獎項<ref name="Rules">{{cite web | title = Rule Thirteen: Special Rules for the Foreign Language Film Award | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | publisher = [[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | accessdate = 2013-08-26 | archive-date = 2013-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130730051948/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，提名電影應在每年10月至翌年9月間於所在[[國家|國家]]或地區公映。該獎僅頒給電影的[[導演|導演]]，但被認為是對出品[[國家|國家]]的獎勵。該獎項原名為「奧斯卡最佳外語片獎」，但學院認為「外語」該詞已過時，所以於2019年4月更名為「最佳國際影片獎」<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527181952/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ACADEMY ANNOUNCES RULES FOR 92ND OSCARS |url=https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Oscars.org {{!}} Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2019-04-23 |language=en |archive-date=2019-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190711223230/https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=options |first1=Show more sharing |last2=URLCopied! |first2=Copy Link |title=Film academy is setting new inclusion standards for Oscars eligibility |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712145159/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Lawler |first1=Kelly |title=Academy to implement diversity standards for Oscars eligibility, set best picture at 10 nominees |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=USA TODAY |archive-date=2021-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829090110/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#1"/>。

1951年至1955年間，日本電影曾獲得三次奧斯卡最佳外語片獎。從1956年開始，最佳外語片獎成為競賽單元，正式制訂評審辦法，並且每年頒獎<ref name="HistPg2">{{cite web|title=History of the Academy Awards - Page 2 |publisher=[[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] |url=http://www.oscars.org/aboutacademyawards/history02.html |accessdate=2008-08-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622191328/http://www.oscars.org/aboutacademyawards/history02.html |archivedate=2008-06-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

直到目前（2022年）為止，日本電影總共入圍過13次奧斯卡最佳外語片獎，位居第五位，僅次於[[法國|法國]]、[[義大利|義大利]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]與[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Foreign Language Film Facts |publisher=[[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts_and_Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] |url=http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/help/statistics/forlangfacts.html |date=2008-03-08 |accessdate=2008-06-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070613115409/http://awardsdatabase.oscars.org/ampas_awards/help/statistics/forlangfacts.html |archivedate=2007-06-13 }}</ref>，其中《[[送行者：禮儀師的樂章|送行者：禮儀師的樂章]]》和《[[在車上|在車上]]》是1956年至2021年間唯二獲得奧斯卡最佳外語片獎的日本電影<ref name="UCLAList">{{cite web|url=http://www.international.ucla.edu/eas/statistics/asian-oscar.htm |title=List of Asian films nominated for Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film |publisher=[[University_of_California,_Los_Angeles|University of California, Los Angeles]] |accessdate=2008-06-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080607164054/http://www.international.ucla.edu/eas/statistics/asian-oscar.htm |archivedate=2008-06-07 }}</ref><ref name="VarietyWinners">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/awardcentral_article/VR1117856491.html?nav=history|title=Best Foreign Film|publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''|author=''Variety'' Staff|date=2007-03-01|accessdate=2008-07-13|archive-date=2012-12-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20121205002943/http://www.variety.com/awardcentral|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

歷年的提交名單當中，只有12部電影同為[[日本電影學院獎|日本電影學院獎]]的「[[日本電影學院獎最佳影片獎|最佳電影]]」，包括《花一錢》、 《魔法公主》 、 《愛之祈求者》、 《鐵道員》、 《下雨了》 、 《黃昏的清兵衛》 、 《扶桑花女孩》 、 《送行者：禮儀師的樂章》 、《告白》、《字裡人間》、《小偷家族》及《在車上》，當中四部電影 《黃昏的清兵衛》、 《送行者：禮儀師的樂章》、 《小偷家族》及《在車上》最後獲得提名。

